title: 5 minute HIIT Workout No Jumping | Beginner Low Impact Exercises
description:
Short on time or just starting out with exercise? Get your body moving and burn fat with this 5 Minute HIIT Workout No Jumping. Here’s the format: 5 beginner low impact exercises in 30 second rounds with 20 seconds of rest. My mom shows how it’s done in a chair! It's about 600 steps, more or less depending on your pace.

Let’s HIIT it!

00:00 Introduction
00:40 Warm Up & Workout
05:09 Cooldown

Want more HIIT workouts? 
Here’s a link to our 5-Minute HIIT Workout #1. Also, check out our full HIIT playlist! https://bit.ly/3MbznVl
